---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Project Umbra">
  <section class="wrap adv-head">
    <span class="kicker">About</span>
    <h1>Project Umbra is an experimental open-source supply-chain security project.</h1>
  </section>

  <article class="wrap prose">
    <p>
      Findings are published here once coordinated disclosure with the vendor is complete.
    </p>

    <h2>Disclosure policy</h2>
    <p>
      We report issues privately to the affected vendor and give them <b>90 days</b> to ship a
      fix before anything is published. The clock starts on first contact. If a vendor responds
      quickly, asks for more time in good faith, or the issue is already being exploited in the
      wild, we adjust the timeline accordingly. Technical detail stays embargoed until disclosure.
    </p>

    <h2>Contributors</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Eu Joe — model, evals, pipeline</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Triage</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Damien Wong — triage, manual review</li>
      <li><em>others TBD</em></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Reports, questions, or coordination: <a href="mailto:joe@cooties.io">joe@cooties.io</a>.
      A PGP key is available on request for sensitive material.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
